snippet.title: Mega Man Shattered Diamond - SAGE 2022 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Mega Man Shattered Diamond is coming to the Sonic Amateur Games Expo, this year! Get ready to play a demo featuring Mega Man, Bass, and 3 of the robot masters.

The demo is live! Check it out here:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/mega-man-shattered-diamond.1334/

Credit to Shinryu for editing the awesome trailer. Check out his channel, he plays Mega Man games!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSl_plnZs6w

You can also get more updates from our social media pages:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TeamCircadia
Discord Server: https://discord.gg/yqra84S
